        "text": "You cry out for aid, and a creature near you feels compelled tothrow itself in front of the threat as the ultimate expressionof their love. A target that genuinely loves the caster withoutmagical compulsion, at their player\u2019s or the GM\u2019s discretion,fails the save.",
